text: Thank you all for being a part of this journey. We wish you happy holidays and all the best for 2019! The Aiir Team

The past year has been very exciting. We spoke at top AI and MRO conventions and continued the development of our product. On top of it all, we were very lucky to work on exciting projects with great companies. We cannot wait to continue this adventure in 2019!

The new year is underway and what a year it will be! Last year we received news that our application for the Take-Off grant was approved. We will use this to continue developing and exploring the market of automating jet engine inspections.

This strengthens our collaboration and allows us to take this innovation to the next level. We look forward to working more closely with the Polytential team and revolutionize plastic recycling!

For the past few months we have been working with Polytential ( https://www. polytential.eu ) to classify types of plastic for recycling purposes, using hyperspectral imaging using AI. We received news that our joint proposal has been accepted!
